@startuml JSON-RPC模块数据流动架构图
title JSON-RPC 模块数据流动架构图

' 定义样式
skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor<<core>> #E3F2FD
    BackgroundColor<<stdio>> #E8F5E9
    BackgroundColor<<http>> #FFF3E0
    BorderColor<<core>> #1976D2
    BorderColor<<stdio>> #388E3C
    BorderColor<<http>> #F57C00
    RoundCorner 10
    BorderThickness 2
}

skinparam arrow {
    Color #546E7A
    Thickness 2
}

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #9E9E9E
}

skinparam message {
    BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
    BorderColor #607D8B
}

' ==================== 布局 ====================

' 左侧：Stdio客户端
rectangle "Stdio 客户端" <<client>> as StdioClient #F5F5F5 {
    rectangle "标准输入 (stdin)" <<stdio>> as Stdin
    rectangle "标准输出 (stdout)" <<stdio>> as Stdout
}

' 中间上：StdioJsonRpc传输层
rectangle "StdioJsonRpc 传输层" <<stdio>> as StdioTransport {
    rectangle "消息读取\n(逐行/LSP格式)" <<stdio>> as StdioRead
    rectangle "消息发送\n(Content-Length)" <<stdio>> as StdioWrite
    rectangle "异步读取线程" <<stdio>> as StdioThread
}

' 中间：JsonRpc核心处理器
rectangle "JsonRpc 核心处理器" <<core>> as Core {
    rectangle "方法注册表\n(Method Registry)" <<core>> as MethodRegistry
    rectangle "请求处理器\n(Request Handler)" <<core>> as RequestHandler
    rectangle "批量请求支持\n(Batch Support)" <<core>> as BatchSupport
    rectangle "错误处理\n(Error Handler)" <<core>> as ErrorHandler
}

' 右侧：HttpJsonRpcServer传输层
rectangle "HttpJsonRpcServer 传输层" <<http>> as HttpTransport {
    rectangle "HTTP POST 处理器" <<http>> as HttpPost
    rectangle "SSE 推送服务" <<http>> as SseServer
    rectangle "线程池管理" <<http>> as ThreadPool
}

' 右侧：HTTP客户端
rectangle "HTTP 客户端" <<client>> as HttpClient #F5F5F5 {
    rectangle "HTTP POST 请求" <<http>> as HttpRequest
    rectangle "SSE 订阅" <<http>> as SseClient
}

' 底部：业务逻辑层
rectangle "业务逻辑方法" <<business>> as Business #F3E5F5 {
    rectangle "工具调用" <<method>> as ToolMethod
    rectangle "资源操作" <<method>> as ResourceMethod
    rectangle "提示管理" <<method>> as PromptMethod
}

' ==================== 数据流：输入 ====================

' Stdio输入流
Stdin -down-> StdioRead : **JSON-RPC请求**
note right of StdioRead
  读取流程：
  1. 解析 Content-Length
  2. 读取完整消息
  3. 验证消息格式
end note

StdioRead -down-> RequestHandler : **解析后的请求**

' HTTP输入流
HttpRequest -down-> HttpPost : **HTTP POST /rpc**
note right of HttpPost
  请求流程：
  1. 接收HTTP请求
  2. 解析JSON body
  3. 提取JSON-RPC消息
end note

HttpPost -down-> RequestHandler : **解析后的请求**

' ==================== 数据流：核心处理 ====================

RequestHandler -down-> MethodRegistry : **查找方法**
MethodRegistry -down-> Business : **执行业务逻辑**

note right of RequestHandler
  核心处理：
  • 单请求/批量请求
  • 通知（无响应）
  • 参数验证
  • 异常捕获
end note

' ==================== 数据流：输出 ====================

' Stdio输出流
Business -up-> StdioWrite : **处理结果**
StdioWrite -up-> Stdout : **JSON-RPC响应**
note left of StdioWrite
  响应格式：
  Content-Length: xxx\n\n
  {json响应}
end note

' HTTP输出流
Business -up-> HttpPost : **处理结果**
HttpPost -up-> HttpRequest : **HTTP 200 响应**

' SSE推送流
Business -right-> SseServer : **实时事件**
SseServer -right-> SseClient : **SSE 数据推送**
note bottom of SseServer
  SSE 格式：
  data: {json}\n\n
  event: 类型\n\n
  id: ID\n\n
end note

' ==================== 图例 ====================

rectangle "图例" as Legend #FFFFFF {
    rectangle "核心处理器" <<core>> as LCore
    rectangle "Stdio传输层" <<stdio>> as LStdio
    rectangle "HTTP传输层" <<http>> as LHttp
    rectangle "业务逻辑" <<business>> as LBusiness
}

note top of Legend
  **数据流方向**
  ↓ 输入流（客户端 → 服务端）
  ↑ 输出流（服务端 → 客户端）
end note

' ==================== 连接线标注 ====================

StdioRead -right-> BatchSupport : 批量处理\n支持
ThreadPool -left-> RequestHandler : 并发请求\n处理
SseServer -left-> ErrorHandler : 错误推送\n通知

@enduml
